---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="The Edgewater Hotel | Luxury Waterfront Hotel in Downtown Seattle"
  description="The Edgewater is Seattle's only over-water hotel, and an iconic downtown luxury Seattle hotel immortalized in rock history by The Beatles."
>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-bg">
      <img
        src="https://admin.edgewaterhotel.com/content/uploads/2025/12/The-Edgewater-Hotel-Seattle-WA-1.jpg"
        alt="The Edgewater Hotel on the waterfront of Elliott Bay, Seattle"
        loading="eager"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="container hero-content">
      <h1>Seattle's Only<br/>Over-Water Hotel</h1>
      <p>Where rock 'n' roll legacy and the unrivaled beauty of the Pacific Northwest meet, stands The Edgewater Hotel. This iconic downtown Seattle hotel, set above the waters of Puget Sound and immortalized in rock history by The Beatles, is your home base for memorable sights, scenic adventures and waterfront charm.</p>
      <div class="hero-cta">
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Book Now</a>
        <a href="#rooms" class="btn btn-outline" style="border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); color: #fff;">Explore Rooms</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Rooms Carousel -->
  <section class="section" id="rooms">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="label">Stay</span>
        <h2>Sleep Easy In Seattle</h2>
        <a href="/stay/" class="view-all">View All Rooms &rarr;</a>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-3 rooms-grid">
        <a href="/stay/beatles-suite/" class="room-card">
          <img
            class="room-card-img"
            src="https://admin.edgewaterhotel.com/content/uploads/2026/01/nhh200-noble-house-edgewater-stay-beatles-2.jpg"
            alt="The Beatles suite at Edgewater with a lounge space and Beatles-inspired bedroom"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <div class="room-card-body">
            <h3>Beatles Suite</h3>
            <div class="room-meta">
              <span>Over-Water</span>
              <span>Specialty</span>
              <span>750 sq ft</span>
            </div>
            <p>Relive a legendary moment in history and stay in the suite made famous by the iconic image of The Beatles fishing out of the window.</p>
            <div class="room-card-actions">
              <span class="btn btn-sand btn-sm">View Details</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>

        <div class="room-card">
          <img
            class="room-card-img"
            src="https://admin.edgewaterhotel.com/content/uploads/2026/01/nhh200-noble-house-edgewater-stay-pearl-jam-10.jpg"
            alt="The Pearl Jam inspired living space at Edgewater"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <div class="room-card-body">
            <h3>Pearl Jam Suite</h3>
            <div class="room-meta">
              <span>Over-Water</span>
              <span>Specialty</span>
              <span>750 sq ft</span>
            </div>
            <p>We partnered with Pearl Jam's Eddie Vedder and their fan club to design the ultimate Seattle band-inspired suite, perfect for music lovers.</p>
            <div class="room-card-actions">
              <span class="btn btn-sand btn-sm">View Details</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="room-card">
          <img
            class="room-card-img"
            src="https://admin.edgewaterhotel.com/content/uploads/2026/02/Edgewater-Overwater-King-with-Balcony.jpg"
            alt="A beautiful Overwater King With Balcony at Edgewater"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <div class="room-card-body">
            <h3>Over-Water King with Balcony</h3>
            <div class="room-meta">
              <span>Over-Water</span>
              <span>350 sq ft</span>
            </div>
            <p>Take in majestic views of the Olympic Mountains from a spacious balcony with Adirondack chairs, then unwind with a plush king bed and cozy fireplace.</p>
            <div class="room-card-actions">
              <span class="btn btn-sand btn-sm">View Details</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Explore Split -->
  <section class="feature-split">
    <img
      class="feature-split-img"
      src="https://admin.edgewaterhotel.com/content/uploads/2026/02/086A9748.jpg"
      alt="A view of Waterfront park and aquarium in Seattle, Washington"
      loading="lazy"
    />
    <div class="feature-split-content section-cream">
      <span class="label">Explore</span>
      <h2>Experience Life at The Edge</h2>
      <p>The Emerald City has it all: world-class sports, famous landmarks and of course, a vibrant music and arts scene. With all that and much more just outside your doorstep, our waterfront hotel is perfectly located to keep you entertained and exploring.</p>
      <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline">Explore Things To Do</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Seasons -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>A City For Every Season</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-4">
        <a href="#" class="season-card">
          <img
            src="https://admin.edgewaterhotel.com/content/uploads/2026/02/Edge_AutumnBarOct2025-7548.jpg"
            alt="Little autumn bar decorated with pumpkins and autumn decor"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <div class="season-card-label"><h3>Fall</h3></div>
        </a>
        <a href="#" class="season-card">
          <img
            src="https://admin.edgewaterhotel.com/content/uploads/2026/02/Mt.RainierCabin-145.jpg"
            alt="Mt. Rainier covered in snow"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <div class="season-card-label"><h3>Winter</h3></div>
        </a>
        <a href="#" class="season-card">
          <img
            src="https://admin.edgewaterhotel.com/content/uploads/2026/02/EdgewaterMarch2024-1580.jpg"
            alt="Flowers at Pike Place Market"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <div class="season-card-label"><h3>Spring</h3></div>
        </a>
        <a href="#" class="season-card">
          <img
            src="https://admin.edgewaterhotel.com/content/uploads/2026/02/T-Mobile-Park-cropped.jpg"
            alt="T-Mobile Park in Seattle"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <div class="season-card-label"><h3>Summer</h3></div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Dining Split -->
  <section class="feature-split reverse">
    <img
      class="feature-split-img"
      src="https://admin.edgewaterhotel.com/content/uploads/2026/02/EdgewaterJune2024-1490.jpg"
      alt="Guests having drinks at the bar at Edgewater"
      loading="lazy"
    />
    <div class="feature-split-content">
      <span class="label">Dine</span>
      <h2>Award-Winning Cuisine & Inspiring Views</h2>
      <p>Savor Pacific Northwest flavors with stunning waterfront views. From the award-winning Six Seven Restaurant to The Brim coffee shop, every dining experience is designed to fuel your Emerald City adventures.</p>
      <a href="/dine/" class="btn btn-outline">Dine With Us</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Offers Split -->
  <section class="feature-split">
    <img
      class="feature-split-img"
      src="https://admin.edgewaterhotel.com/content/uploads/2025/12/nhh200-noble-house-edgewater-offers3.jpg"
      alt="Lounge area at The Edgewater with a view of the water and a fireplace"
      loading="lazy"
    />
    <div class="feature-split-content section-sand">
      <span class="label">Offers & Packages</span>
      <h2>Elevate Your Stay</h2>
      <p>Make the most of your time in the Pacific Northwest with special offers and exclusive packages designed to elevate your stay at our boutique waterfront hotel in Seattle.</p>
      <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline">View All Offers</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Events CTA -->
  <section class="feature-split reverse">
    <img
      class="feature-split-img"
      src="https://admin.edgewaterhotel.com/content/uploads/2026/02/nhh200-noble-house-edgewater-meetings-events-1.jpg"
      alt="An empty wedding space setup at Edgewater"
      loading="lazy"
    />
    <div class="feature-split-content">
      <span class="label">Gather</span>
      <h2>Meet Your Ideal Event Planning Partner</h2>
      <p>With panoramic views of Puget Sound as your backdrop, The Edgewater blends exceptional ambiance, personalized service and memorable cuisine to create weddings, meetings and events that feel truly one-of-a-kind.</p>
      <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline">Start Planning</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Spring Promo Banner -->
  <section class="cta-banner">
    <div class="hero-bg">
      <img
        src="https://admin.edgewaterhotel.com/content/uploads/2026/02/086A9702.jpg"
        alt="Seattle Great Wheel on the waterfront"
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="container cta-banner-content">
      <span class="label" style="color: var(--sand); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; display: block;">Limited Time</span>
      <h2>Seattle In Bloom</h2>
      <p>Celebrate spring in the Emerald City. Book our "Seattle in Bloom" offer by March 26 to enjoy up to 25% off our best available rates, plus a $50 credit to The Brim.</p>
      <a href="#" class="btn btn-sand">Book Now</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .hero-cta {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .section-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .section-header .label {
    color: var(--warm-gray);
  }
  .view-all {
    margin-left: auto;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--warm-gray);
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .view-all:hover { color: var(--charcoal); }
  .rooms-grid .room-card { text-decoration: none; }
</style>
